Update:
1. Simulasi Ujian menggunakan database.

Format database:
Nama database = mydatabase

Nama table = nilaiipa1

Nama field,Type,Length/value = nama,TEXT,
                               nis,VARCHAR,4
                               passw,VARCHAR,8
                               nilai,FLOAT,

Isi field (nama, nis, passw, nilai) = yosua, 0001, 08101996, -1
                                      andre, 0002, 28091997, -1
                                      chandra, 0003, 03031996, -1
                                      arman, 0004, 25121996, -1
            
